quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"L Nabiyow! Ku Rabbi dakanu leh у an marak kah abenna Matablannaa?"
  105,2,"Yalli Ken urna mala fïnqa maabinnaa?"
  105,3,"Kaadu haadâ butta buttah keenit ruube itta kataatak"
  105,4,"Xeetiy cararte kallak yani keenil qambissa."
  105,5,"tokkel ruma yekke caffaa kee cafulay yonkommeh inna ken abe."
